OL,3,CThree men jailed after series of
OL,4,Crobberies
OL,6,FThree men who carried out a series of
OL,7,Frobberies in Derby have been jailed
OL,8,Ffor more than 14 years.
OL,10,FChristopher Jackson carried out a
OL,11,Fstring of robberies in Derby city
OL,12,Fcentre between September and October
OL,13,F2022.
OL,15,FHe forced two of his victims to
OL,16,Fwithdraw money from cashpoints at
OL,17,Fknifepoint, and held a pair of
OL,18,Fscissors to another man's throat as he
OL,19,Fsearched him for money.
