OL,6,FOn the 24th September, he and his
OL,7,Faccomplice Peter Kearney targeted
OL,8,FHarrys Amusements in the Morledge in
OL,9,Fthe city.
OL,11,FKearney was armed with a pair of
OL,12,Fscissors and the pair threatened to
OL,13,Fstab a member of staff if she did not
OL,14,Fhand over cash. The pair escaped with
OL,15,Fa significant amount of money.
OL,17,FAnd on the 12th October, Jackson, with
OL,18,Faccomplice Lessan Duhaney, robbed a
OL,19,Fvulnerable man at his home in the Five
OL,20,FLamps area of the city.
