OL,3,CThree men jailed after series of
OL,4,Crobberies
OL,6,F"Armed with knives and scissors they
OL,7,Fsubjected their victims to terrifying
OL,8,Fexperiences where they were told that
OL,9,Fthey would be stabbed if they didn't
OL,10,Fcomply with their demands.
OL,12,F"Excellent teamwork meant that each of
OL,13,Fthe offences could be linked and
OL,14,Fprovided such a strong case that both
OL,15,FJackson and Kearney pleaded guilty
OL,16,Fbefore trial.
OL,18,F"I welcome the sentences handed to
OL,19,Fthem which mean the public will be
OL,20,Fprotected from three dangerous
OL,21,Findividuals for some time."
